---
title: Teriyaki Pork Belly Burger & Kumara Fries with Asian Pear Slaw & Mayonnaise
description: This twist on a burger is our most decadent invention yet. Pork belly, known for its rich, melt-in-your-mouth texture and irresistible flavour, is getting a teriyaki-flavoured makeover before being sandwiched in the middle of a perfectly toasted bun. This Asian-style burger is a flavour fusion you won’t want to miss!
